title: Kunara Organic Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The deli case of dishes change daily and features salads, sandwiches, savories and sweets. Breakfast all day includes muesli with nut mylk and fruit compote. Organic coffee made with pure spring water and served with your choice of milk.
